_em_vitrification.details               
;To prepare cryo-grids, 3 ul samples were applied to glow discharged Quantifoil Au grids (R2/2, 300 mesh), which were subsequently blotted with filter paper (Ted Pella) for 3 seconds at 18oC and 100% humidity. The grids were immediately plunge frozen in liquid ethane using a FEI Vitrobot IV (ThermoFisher)
